name: WaykiChain
description: WaykiChain (WICC) is a third-generation blockchain that is based on DPoS consensus algorithms and supports Turing-complete smart contracts. It is reportedly able to sustain transactional throughput above 1,000 TPS in actual use. In the long run, WaykiChain (WICC) aims to provide a secure, reliable and high-performant blockchain technology platform that will enable the growth of multiple industries such as prediction markets, decentralized assets exchanges, and decentralized forex exchanges.
